	 			<div>
	 				<h3>Why Age Alone?</h3>
	 				<h5>When is it time to call Golden View Senior Services?</h5>
	 				<p>The time to call is when you answer "yes" to one or more of the following questions</p>
	 				<ul style="list-style-type: circle;">
	 					<li><p>Does my going to appointments, or shopping depend on the kindness of a neighbor or friend?</p>
	 						<p style="padding-left: 10px;">Our caregivers will drive you to your destinations. Take you
	 							to your doctor's appointments and pickup your groceries for you.</p>
	 					</li>
	 					<li><p>Is cooking or cleaning for myself a burden, or to difficult due to my age?</p>
	 						<p style="padding-left: 10px;">Your meals will be prepared by our caregivers and they will provide light
	 							cleaning of your home.</p>
	 					</li>
	 					<li><p>Do I forget to take my medications, or the correct dosages, due to the directions being too confusing?</p>
	 						<p style="padding-left: 10px;">Our caregivers will make sure that you take your medications on schedule
	 							and our caregivers are licensed and bonded so they will know how to read the directions for your
	 							medication to ensure you get the proper dosages.</p>
	 					</li>
	 					<li><p>Has going for a walk or simply being home alone become too risky?</p>
	 						<p style="padding-left: 10px;">You will never be left alone for too long their will always be a caregiver
	 							their when you need them. You will still have control of your life so you will not be given strict
	 							rules as you would in a facility.</p>
	 					</li>
	 					<li><p>Has your family become too busy in their own lives to assist you in your daily needs?</p>
	 						<p style="padding-left: 10px;">Our caregivers will be their for you to assist you with any of you daily
	 							chores and other activites.</p>
	 					</li>
	 				</ul>
